Package hsrt.mec.controldeveloper.io

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IOType
    Interface IOType defines the methods for reading and writing data into a data stream.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Console
    Console reads strings from the keyboard and writes strings to the console.
    ObjectFile
    ObjectFile serializes the strings given by the Vector and writes them into the given file or reads them out of the file, respectively. important is that the classes, whose objects shall be serialized, implement the interface Serializable (what the class String does).
    TextFile
    TextFile writes strings into a plain text file.
    WiFi
    Read and Write string data to Input/Output Streams attached to TCP Socket session.
